A combination of;

- Rotate by the given angles
- x = abs(x+Fold) - abs(x-Fold) - x
- RotateBack by the given angles

It's a generalization of Tglad's folding formula (on a single direction).
"X" is purely conventional, because any direction can be used changing the angles!